msgctxt "56_Akiyama"
msgid "That just leaves your hair, makeup, and nails."
msgstr "Ahora solo falta el cabello, el maquillaje y las uñas."

msgctxt "68_Akiyama"
msgid "You mind going it alone from here? All that will probably take a while."
msgstr "¿Te importaría ir por tu cuenta? Puede que tome tiempo."

msgctxt "80_Akiyama"
msgid "Just tell them Akiyama said to put it on Sky Finance's tab."
msgstr "Diles que dije que lo pusieran a nombre de Sky Finance."

msgctxt "92_Lily"
msgid "Thank you."
msgstr "Gracias."

msgctxt "104_Akiyama"
msgid "Meet me over at Elise once you're done. It's right across the street from the Millennium Tower. I'll be waiting for you."
msgstr "Nos vemos en el Elise cuando hayas terminado. Está frente a la Torre Millenium. Te estaré esperando."

msgctxt "116_Lily"
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "Está bien."

